es.upm.gib.eutilsrdfwrapper.motor
Class InternalQueryState

java.lang.Object
  es.upm.gib.eutilsrdfwrapper.motor.InternalQueryState

public class InternalQueryState
extends java.lang.Object

This class stores the state of a query in the NCBI database system. It actually stores the result tree. For each database, a QueryListElement is maintained: database, queryKey, index and count. The first element is always a fake database with zero results. This element stores the global EUtils webenv in both the database and queryKey elements
